-- Danske Bank lags in Nordic customer satisfaction, Handelsbanken leads
-- 
-- Wed Oct 08, 2014 08:39AM EDT
-- None



COPENHAGEN, Oct 8 (Reuters) - Svenska Handelsbanken <SHBa.ST> has the most satisfied private customers among top Nordic banks, while those of Danske Bank <DANSKE.CO> are the least satisfied in two of the region's four main markets, surveys from rating agency EPSI showed.

Handelsbanken toped the list in Denmark and Finland and was runner-up in Sweden and Norway behind Lansforsakringar Bank and Skandiabanken respectively. Danske Bank was at the bottom of the list in its Danish home market and in Finland, but finnished ahead of Swedbank <SWEDa.ST> and Nordea <NDA.ST> in Sweden and of DNB <DNB.OL> in the Norwegian market. Handelsbanken also tops the list in Sweden, Denmark and Finland when it comes to satisfaction among corporate customers.